<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <ul class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>I verbi <strong>dovere, potere e volere</strong> sono chiamati <strong class="text-blue-600">verbi servili</strong> perché possono accompagnare un altro verbo (coniugato all'infinito) e formare con esso un unico predicato verbale → <em>Devo comprare</em> (predicato verbale) <em>un giubbotto.</em> → <em>Vuoi provare</em> (predicato verbale) <em>il mio?</em></span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Dovere, potere e volere possono anche essere usati da soli, con un <strong class="text-green-600">significato proprio</strong> → <em>Paola vuole</em> (predicato verbale) <em>un gelato con la panna.</em></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold mr-2">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Scrivi S se il verbo evidenziato è usato come servile, P se è usato con significato proprio.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <strong>Vuoi</strong> fare i compiti con loro?</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_1" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_1" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Isa <strong>può</strong> restare a cena da noi?</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_2" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_2" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Ti <strong>devo</strong> prestare quel romanzo.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_3" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_3" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Max <strong>vuole</strong> un'altra fetta di torta.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_4" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_4" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Mi <strong>devi</strong> un favore!</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_5" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_5" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Non <strong>potete</strong> dire queste bugie.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_6" value="S" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">S</span></label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_6" value="P" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">P</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Complete with servili -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Completa con le forme dei verbi servili adatte.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Il sole è accecante e</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="devo" data-correct-answer="devo" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">indossare gli occhiali.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Corro!</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="Devo" data-correct-answer="Devo" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">essere a casa alle tre.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Se</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="vuoi" data-correct-answer="vuoi" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">giocare, prima</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="devi" data-correct-answer="devi" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">finire i compiti.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Voi</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="potete" data-correct-answer="potete" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">prestarmi una penna?</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Sofia non</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="può" data-correct-answer="può" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">venire con noi.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Luca</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="deve" data-correct-answer="deve" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">allenarsi molto se</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="vuole" data-correct-answer="vuole" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">battere il record.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
      Scrivi sul quaderno una frase con ciascuno dei seguenti verbi accompagnandoli con un verbo servile.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        regalare
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        correre
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        inviare
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        prendere
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
